---
const name = "Travis Wooley";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Home | Travis Wooley" active="home">

<section class="hero">

  <p class="eyebrow">
    Operations Leadership • Manufacturing Systems • AI-Driven Workflow Automation
  </p>

  <h1>Travis Wooley</h1>

  <h2>
    I build and scale technical operations systems that improve reliability, speed, and cost efficiency in manufacturing environments.
  </h2>

  <p class="hero-text">
    I specialize in taking complex, high-variability operational environments—like industrial manufacturing and refurbishment systems—and turning them into structured, scalable, data-driven workflows.
  </p>

  <div class="hero-buttons">
    <a class="button primary" href="/projects">View Work</a>
    <a class="button secondary" href="/resume">Experience</a>
  </div>

</section>

<section>

<h2>What I Do</h2>

<div class="card">
  <p>
    I lead technical operations programs where reliability, throughput, and quality directly impact cost and customer outcomes.
  </p>

  <p>
    My work focuses on building systems—not just executing tasks:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Designing end-to-end refurbishment and manufacturing workflows</li>
    <li>Building internal tools that eliminate operational bottlenecks</li>
    <li>Creating structured quality systems for repeatable output</li>
    <li>Leading teams in high-precision engineering environments</li>
  </ul>
</div>

</section>

<section>

<h2>Core Impact</h2>

<div class="stats">

  <div class="stat">
    <h3>7-Figure</h3>
    <p>Annual cost savings through refurbishment systems</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stat">
    <h3>300+</h3>
    <p>Industrial systems processed annually</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stat">
    <h3>10+ Years</h3>
    <p>Manufacturing & engineering operations experience</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stat">
    <h3>Systems</h3>
    <p>Built internal AI + workflow automation tools</p>
  </div>

</div>

</section>

<section>

<h2>Selected Work</h2>

<div class="card">

  <h3>RMA Refurbishment System</h3>
  <p>
    Built and scaled an industrial refurbishment operation from the ground up, turning returned hardware into certified production-ready systems.
  </p>

  <p>
    Established workflows, SOPs, quality inspection systems, vendor networks, and training processes that enabled scalable throughput and consistent output quality.
  </p>

  <a class="button primary" href="/projects">View Case Study</a>

</div>

<div class="card">

  <h3>Internal AI Operations Tool (Build OS)</h3>
  <p>
    Developed an internal AI-assisted workflow system that connects SOPs, inventory, and troubleshooting data into a unified operational interface.
  </p>

  <p>
    Reduced diagnostic friction and improved technician decision-making speed in day-to-day operations.
  </p>

  <a class="button secondary" href="/projects">See Details</a>

</div>

</section>

</MainLayout>